1. help purple (Those entries should exist)
<root> * eionrobb-msteams-personal (Teams (Personal))
<root> * eionrobb-msteams (Teams (Work and School))

2. account add eionrobb-msteams <email>

3. account <email> set nick_format %full_name
   then enter: save

4. account <email> on

5. Register locally for Bitlbee:
   register <password>

6. Next connection:
   identify <password> or /oper <username> <password>
